9 COMMITTEE AMENDMENT “ ” to S.P. 283, L.D. 599, “An Act to Codify the
10 Federal Salary Threshold for Overtime Pay”
11 Amend the bill by striking out the title and substituting the following:
12 'An Act to Raise the Salary Threshold for Overtime Pay'
13 Amend the bill by inserting after section 1 the following:
14 'Sec. 2. Appropriations and allocations. The following appropriations and
15 allocations are made.
16 ADMINISTRATIVE AND FINANCIAL SERVICES, DEPARTMENT OF
17 Executive Branch Departments and Independent Agencies - Statewide 0017
18 Initiative: Provides ongoing funds for the additional overtime costs associated with
19 increasing the annual rate that an employee who works in an executive, administrative or
20 professional capacity must earn in order to be exempt from the laws governing the
21 minimum wage and overtime pay to a minimum of $58,656 effective January 1, 2026.
