COMMITTEE AMENDMENT

COMMITTEE AMENDMENT “ ” to S.P. 283, L.D. 599
1 Amend the bill by relettering or renumbering any nonconsecutive Part letter or section
2 number to read consecutively.
3 SUMMARY
44 This amendment is the majority report of the committee. The amendment changes the
55 title, adds an appropriations and allocations section and adds an effective date of January
66 1, 2026.
